    "created_at": "2012-12-03T19:14:09Z",
    "updated_at": "2012-12-03T19:14:09Z",
    "body": "The removal of `get_ref` grew out of trying to make #4020 work, but as I commented in that bug I think the idea of a \"resettable future\" is itself nonsensical and should be reformed to use `pipe::oneshot`. I'll update this to leave `get_ref` in and remove `with` and, I think, close the other one. Agreed?\n",
